const HERO_TEXT = [
  "a universal flow of energy and creativity that connects us all",
  "manifesting that flow of energy using whatever it brings",
  "listening and responding to each encounter",
  "art is an opportunity to respond and connect with the moment",
  "art is a stimulating conversation wating to be had"
]

export default HERO_TEXT;
